{"tid":93607,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑操作不當致爆谷機爆炸　河南六旬翁傷重亡","createTime":"2017-01-24T14:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T03:35:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"137cba01673d8e5bd4c62952dc52f0aef9537cb7","tid":93607,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170124/photo/bkncn-20170124171136704-0124_05011_001_03p.jpg?20170124174134\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170124%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170124171136704-0124_05011_001_03p.jpg%3F20170124174134&h=f0bd6da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n河南安陽縣白壁鎮張家莊村昨日發生一宗罕見意外，一名60多歲老翁在街邊擺攤售賣爆谷，疑因操作不當致爆谷機發生爆炸，造成老翁頭部重創，最終傷重身亡。有網傳消息指有民眾曾致電120求助，惟未有及時派人前來為老翁救援。 <br />\n<br />\n從網傳現場短片所見，爆炸發生後，老翁倒地不起，其頭部大量出血，地上留有大灘血漬。事發後現場有不少民眾駐足圍觀，有市民上前用布為老翁止血。另網傳消息指，該名老翁希望能在春節前後賺錢過年，於是在街上擺攤售賣爆谷，卻發生爆炸。意外發生後，有民眾致電打120求助，「人家說沒空，後來叫安陽三院救護車來，惟三院離現場相距十萬八千里」，質疑當局未及時前來為老翁搶救。"},{"pid":"8436b296cbf379b02ccb97105c6cfd535e348855","tid":93607,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:16:01.000Z","msg":"支那仲有咩死法未試過"},{"pid":"2a836a4af0bc099c616d71d5ffa0e97df799493a","tid":93607,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"又死一隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16dcb3a25c8845191512160a6b201747626c6583","tid":93607,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"真係爆谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d19e464873e6830e048fde3f1e7dca8550edcf","tid":93607,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T20:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be807e1321a1fc51d19efb8ecfcc91a2ba51cc0a","tid":93607,